{
  "text": ". In the final results, the relative expression levels were determined by the 2 -\u0394Ct method. Statistical significance was tested using Student's t test (P < 0.05) [CITATION_1] . Each PCR product was evaluated in at least two independent experiments. The primers used for semiquantitative PCR and quantitative real-time PCR are listed in Table 2 .",
